import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react";
import LoadingBar from "../LoadingBar/LoadingBar";
import {
  Isprobaj,
  IsprobajResults,
  IsprobajWrapper,
  LoadingBarTitle,
  IsprobajInput,
  IsprobajResultsContainer,
  InputTemperatura,
} from "./IsprobajElements";

function Test() {
  const [barPercentage, setbarPercentage] = useState(2000);

  return (
    <Isprobaj id="isprobaj">
      <IsprobajInput>
        <InputTemperatura type="text"></InputTemperatura>
      </IsprobajInput>
      <IsprobajResultsContainer id="test1">
        <IsprobajResults>
          <IsprobajWrapper>
            <LoadingBarTitle>Temperature</LoadingBarTitle>
            <LoadingBar
              min_progress="0"
              max_progress="6000"
              title="Temperature"
              done={barPercentage}
            />
          </IsprobajWrapper>
          <IsprobajWrapper>
            <LoadingBarTitle>Temperature</LoadingBarTitle>
            <LoadingBar
              min_progress="0"
              max_progress="6000"
              title="Temperature"
              done={barPercentage}
            />
          </IsprobajWrapper>
          <IsprobajWrapper>
            <LoadingBarTitle>Temperature</LoadingBarTitle>
            <LoadingBar
              min_progress="0"
              max_progress="6000"
              title="Temperature"
              done={barPercentage}
            />
          </IsprobajWrapper>
          <IsprobajWrapper>
            <LoadingBarTitle>Temperature</LoadingBarTitle>
            <LoadingBar
              min_progress="0"
              max_progress="6000"
              title="Temperature"
              done={barPercentage}
            />
          </IsprobajWrapper>
          <IsprobajWrapper>
            <LoadingBarTitle>Temperature</LoadingBarTitle>
            <LoadingBar
              min_progress="0"
              max_progress="6000"
              title="Temperature"
              done={barPercentage}
            />
          </IsprobajWrapper>
        </IsprobajResults>
      </IsprobajResultsContainer>
    </Isprobaj>
  );
}

export default Test;
